    "summary": "Our law firm was founded on a deep-seated passion to help others so that they can smoothly navigate all aspects of Dutch corporate employment law.\n\nWe do so as a consistent, distinctive and compact team of highly specialised, committed advisors, with numerous years of collective experience at global firms (BakerMcKenzie and Linklaters).\n\nWhat do we offer?\n\n1. Transactional support\n2. Strategic advice\n3. Litigation capabilities\n\nOthers say that we add value when advising our clients on delicate and high profile (executive) dismissals, restrictive covenants issues, works council consultation processes, collective redundancies and business restructurings (including negotiations with trade unions and/or works councils on social plans).\n\nThey also praise our strong track record and strengths:\n\n* fostering personal relationships with companies and executives;\n* being consistent and pragmatic, business oriented, focused and well networked;\n* getting things done, cutting through to key issues;\n* providing sound judgement, not just technical expertise.\n\nIn short: we are the unique boutique focusing solely on Dutch corporate employment law.\n\nOur clients are internationally operating corporates and high-level executives.\n\nI have lived in El Salvador, Singapore, Brazil and on St. Maarten. I also tap into a broad (inter)national network, having worked at said global law firms and at leading Dutch firm Houthoff.\n\nIndependent legal directories Chambers and Partners and The Legal 500 rank our firm as one of Europe's leading firms for business and rank me as a leading lawyer in my field. Sources quoted (from 2014 to 2023) say:\n\n\"Noteworthy firm with proven expertise in the employment aspects of M&A transactions and individual dismissal matters\"\n\n\"Martijn is a pleasure to work with. He is balanced, understands client needs and is extremely knowledgeable about Dutch legislation\"\n\n\"Really responsive, experienced, commercial and knowledgeable\"\u200b\n\n\"Business oriented, pleasant and factual\"\n\n\"An effective negotiator\u201d\n\n\"He brings relevant experience and deep knowledge\"\n\n\"He proactively drives towards a good outcome\"\n\n\"A high level of clarity in communication\u201d\n\n\u201cSkillful and amicable\"\n\n\"Helpful and prompt\"\n\n\"An excellent team\"\n\n\"The lawyers have a good understanding of M&A\" and \"provide advice without allowing the heat of he situation to interfere with timing and decisions\"\n\n\"Quick turnaround, clear communications and guidance\"",
